    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Besides these given great answers, What I have learned is that:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>NEVER compare objects with == unless you intend to be comparing them\n  by their references.</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
