    "question_id" : 3637936,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>As well for correctness of using <code>==</code> you can just unbox one of compared <code>Integer</code> values before doing <code>==</code> comparison, like:</p>\n\n<pre><code>if ( firstInteger.intValue() == secondInteger ) {..\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>The second will be auto unboxed (of course you have to check for <code>null</code>s first).</p>\n"
